						<summary>

						<p>Image of Hanumān in front of the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1464, Dundubhi, Māgha ba. 13, Thursday,</hi> Irregular.</p>						

						<p>Records the consecration of the image of Hanumān at Bhōgavōlu by Chennama Nāyuḍu, son of Paḍāla Andanayya.</p>						

